==English==

===Etymology===
From Middle English ''[[tigre]]'' < Old English ''[[tigras|tīgras]]'' ({{p}}) and influenced by Old French ''[[tigre]]'', both < Latin ''[[tigris]]'' < Greek [[τίγρις]], possibly of Iranian origin.

